c: 17
v: 107
t: "Nabiyow! ama korosuk ixxic: isin ama Qhuraan nummaysa, hinnay kaa manummaysina, tokkel isin kaa nummassaanam tu kaat moosissaay isin kaa dirabbossaanam tu kaak (Qhuraan kinnuk) madaggossak, diggah kaak duma naharsi kitooba kah tontocowwime maray (yahuud kee nasaarâ tutaaxagok yeemene mara kinnuk) wacyi numma kinnim yeexege usuk (Qhuraan kinnuk) keenil yankirriyime waqdi Yallah kummaatak gomboh radan kaah Rammitak"